Name:          Nikola Tesla
Lived:         1856 - 1943
Nationality:   Serbian-American
Field:         Engineering
Known For:     AC electricity, induction motor
Contribution:  Alternating current power systems; Tesla coil; radio foundation
Quote:         "The present is theirs; the future is mine."

Name:          Tim Berners-Lee
Lived:         1955 - present
Nationality:   English
Field:         Computing
Known For:     World Wide Web
Contribution:  Invented the Web in 1989; gave it to the world for free
Quote:         "The web does not just connect machines, it connects people."

Name:          Aristotle
Lived:         384 - -322
Nationality:   Greek
Field:         Philosophy
Known For:     Logic, ethics, biology
Contribution:  Codified logic; wrote on biology, physics, ethics, politics; tutored Alexander
Quote:         "The more you know, the more you know you don't know."

